parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock up, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The power steering warning light illuminates
the steering wheel feels stiff or hard to turn
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel shakes or vibrates
the vehicle is difficult to control
and the power steering assist message is displayed on the instrument panel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the steering wheel to lock up, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels loose or has excessive play
the steering wheel clicks or makes a knocking noise
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
and the steering column shakes or vibrates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPS system can cause the power steering assist message to be displayed on the instrument panel, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The power steering assist message is displayed on the instrument panel
the power steering warning light illuminates
the steering wheel feels stiff or hard to turn
and the EPS system fails to provide power assistance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause various safety issues, such as loss of power, faulty brake lights, and malfunctioning air conditioning, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Intermittent or complete loss of electrical system functions
faulty brake lights
malfunctioning air conditioning
faulty door locks
and faulty headlights.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake light failures can cause accidents or near-misses, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's intentions to stop.
symptoms: Brake lights fail to illuminate
brake lights stay on continuously
or brake lights malfunction intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling and reduced power can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: Engine stalling
reduced power
and warning lights illuminating on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission and suspension issues can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Transmission failure
suspension problems
and unusual noises or vibrations while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission shifter cable can cause the vehicle to become stuck in gear, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The gear shifter feels loose or stuck
the vehicle is stuck in gear
the vehicle will not shift into gear
the transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Issues (Slipping, Hesitation, Failure to Engage)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission issues can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle loses power or stalls
the vehicle will not shift into gear
the transmission makes unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electronic Stability Control (ESC) and Traction Control Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ESC and traction control systems can cause the vehicle to lose traction, making it difficult to control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ESC and traction control warning lights illuminate
the vehicle loses traction
the vehicle vibrates or shakes
the vehicle's power is reduced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of power steering assist can make it difficult to steer the vehicle, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The power steering assist is lost
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle is hard to maneuver.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake issues can cause the vehicle to vibrate or lose control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle vibrates when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical issues can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the engine light illuminates
the vehicle's electrical systems malfunction.
